videos.description: TJ Haws recovers after biting on the shot fake and makes the great block to force the shot clock violation, BYU trails Saint Mary's in the first half.
videos.headline: Second effort leads to block for BYU

videos.description: Evan Fitzner finds Joe Rahon in the corner for the 3-pointer to extend Saint Marys' lead over BYU.
videos.headline: Extra pass sets up corner 3-pointer for Saint Mary's

videos.description: BYU's Yoeli Childs throws an errant pass towards his head coach, Dave Rose, who is standing by the team's bench.
videos.headline: Don't throw to the guy in the tie!

videos.description: Calvin Hermanson scores a game-high 17 points and No. 22 Saint Mary's defeats BYU 70-57.
videos.headline: Saint Mary's takes down BYU
